==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: fire-tree
<hw>fire-tree</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a terrestrial evergreen shrub or
small tree (<spn>Nuytsia floribunda</spn>) of West Australia having
brilliant yellow-orange flowers; parasitic on roots of
grasses.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> flame tree, flame-tree, Christmas tree, <spn>Nuytsia
floribunda</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

